io.sarl.lang.scoping.batch

Class SARLMapExtensions

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.sarl.lang.scoping.batch.SARLMapExtensions

  • @GwtCompatible
public final class SARLMapExtensions
extends Object
    This is an extension library for maps in the SARL language.

    This extension is provided for the elements that are not (yet) provided by the Xbase API. FIXME: Remove if Xbase or Xtend are providing these functions.

    Version:
    $FullVersion$
    Author:
    $Author: sgalland$
